to run the tests type
- docker-compose run phpunit 
or 
- docker-compose up

docker-compose run phpunit will just run the unit tests only

To make a test, they must be in the folder "tests"
The test my end in the letters "Test.php"
eg. MyTest.php TheTest.php Test1Test.php

This config can be changed in the phpunit.xml

To make a test, the function must start with the word "test"
eg. public funtion testMyCurrentTest()